Unai Emery on finding the right formation: &ldquo;I used the information from the last two years [under Wenger]. This team played with a three, with a four [at-the-back].&rdquo; [@Football_LDN] #afc<br />
<br />
Emery: &ldquo;Mesut can play right or left or as a #10 in different systems, also with Ramsey playing with three or two, getting in the opposition box. I think players are very open in their mind to playing in different positions to help us, giving us big performances &amp; good attitude.&rdquo;
